{"tid":1602601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［北角炮台山手足小心］見到有「急救員」係狗車陣入面嘅私家車內","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:57.000Z","uid":290205,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0e014289a69d386452718a8bad137cfc03a8be","tid":1602601,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"經過英皇道見到有大概四架狗車，每架狗車中間夾住一架私家車。三架私家車號碼如下：<br />\nUW6524<br />\nVT9854<br />\nTE7942<br />\n<br />\n見到UW6524副駕位坐住身穿急救員背心嘅人士，十成九又係黑警「喬裝成不同人士」。屌佢老母。<br />\n<br />\n但係我頭先好攰唔記得左影相，各位屌細力d，我都係想手足平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a932e0e92b78cd697aaa6496c8770d2e3ea9591f","tid":1602601,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d94d1052aa2c60b671372f95b9bb07fc9d68ba","tid":1602601,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf024715358bbabfd4332aa193ec77b18c0000c","tid":1602601,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"99313fe6af36fd2f33d071393cf49e7d2174d257","tid":1602601,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推下行動Post !!!!!<br />\n<br />\n聽日三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602351/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602351/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n[緊急]9.30三罷！同我推上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601254/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601254/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e57b5c27af85609e076e3900688be9eb58672468","tid":1602601,"uid":78458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019